上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Billie-Eilish-and-Donald-Trump.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-and-Chip-Somodevilla-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="比莉·艾利什和唐纳德·特朗普。图片来源：Kevin Mazur 和 Chip Somodevilla，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Billie-Eilish-and-Donald-Trump.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-and-Chip-Somodevilla-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Billie-Eilish-and-Donald-Trump.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-and-Chip-Somodevilla-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Billie-Eilish-and-Donald-Trump.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-and-Chip-Somodevilla-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Billie-Eilish-and-Donald-Trump.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-and-Chip-Somodevilla-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Billie-Eilish-and-Donald-Trump.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-and-Chip-Somodevilla-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Billie-Eilish-and-Donald-Trump.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-and-Chip-Somodevilla-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump)</a>在 2024 年总统选举中获胜后，娱乐界的多位人士都对他在妇女权利问题上的立场表示担忧。</p><p>这位共和党候选人、前总统赢得了 279 张选举团票，击败了民主党候选人<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/kamala-harris">卡马拉·哈里斯的</a>223 张选举团票。<em> </em>确保他返回白宫（来自<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/c62l5zdv7zko" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>BBC 新闻</em></a>）。</p><p>特朗普的胜利将使他成为 130 多年来第一位重返总统职位的前总统，并以 78 岁高龄创造历史，成为当选美国最高职位的最年长人士。</p><p>现在，特朗普获胜后，娱乐界的许多人物都表达了他们对女性和生殖权利的恐惧和担忧。昂克莱恩·哈里斯（Unkline Harris）是一位直言不讳的领导人和生殖自由的倡导者，特朗普庆祝罗伊诉韦德案的推翻，该案结束了宪法规定的堕胎权，并允许各州完全禁止或严格限制堕胎。</p><p> <a href="/artists/Billie-Eilish">Billie Eilish</a>在她的 Instagram 故事中分享了她对再次当选的第 47 任总统的看法。 “这是一场针对女性的战争”她写道。 “羽毛之鸟”此前在哈里斯最近的一场演出的 Instagram 帖子中分享了她对哈里斯的认可，她告诉观众：“时代真的很可怕，很多事情都处于危险之中，我知道如果你在这个节目中，房间里，你们支持我，你们支持女性，我希望你们投票给卡马拉·哈里斯。”</p><p>帖子的标题是：“不要让任何人告诉你，你的声音和你的投票并不重要！投票给卡玛拉·哈里斯。” </p><figure id="attachment_3810314" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3810314" style="width: 1500px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3810314" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Screengrab-of-Billie-Eilish-Instagram-story.-Credit-Billie-Eilishs-offiical-Instagram-story.jpg" alt="Billie Eilish Instagram 故事的屏幕截图。图片来源：Billie Eilish 的 Instagram 官方故事" width="1500" height="2524" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Screengrab-of-Billie-Eilish-Instagram-story.-Credit-Billie-Eilishs-offiical-Instagram-story.jpg 1500w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Screengrab-of-Billie-Eilish-Instagram-story.-Credit-Billie-Eilishs-offiical-Instagram-story-400x673.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Screengrab-of-Billie-Eilish-Instagram-story.-Credit-Billie-Eilishs-offiical-Instagram-story-800x1346.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Screengrab-of-Billie-Eilish-Instagram-story.-Credit-Billie-Eilishs-offiical-Instagram-story-696x1171.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Screengrab-of-Billie-Eilish-Instagram-story.-Credit-Billie-Eilishs-offiical-Instagram-story-1392x2342.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Screengrab-of-Billie-Eilish-Instagram-story.-Credit-Billie-Eilishs-offiical-Instagram-story-1068x1797.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3810314" class="wp-caption-text"> Billie Eilish 的 Instagram 故事的屏幕截图。图片来源：Billie Eilish 的官方 Instagram 故事</figcaption></figure><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DB-B88rxKx4/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0